headline: 3 Reliable Dividend Stocks Offering Up To 5.2% Yield
summary: As the U.S. stock market grapples with a tech sector slump and investors await crucial insights from Federal Reserve Chair Jerome Powell, many are turning their attention to more stable investment options like dividend stocks. In times of market volatility, reliable dividend stocks can offer a steady income stream and potentially cushion against broader economic uncertainties.
